node.text:
Did you know? Beatrice quit her 9.5 corporate jobs to follow her passions and she is now a freelance content designer and network marketer exploring Mexico. She aspires to help adventurous souls to create a strong brand online and guiding you to find balance between work, sustainable travel and connections. 

She has been selected to go to Antarctica to find solutions to climate change and plastic pollution through education with top leaders.

Here is her page @bea.ventures to follow the adventure, thank me later!

node.text:
@deepak_karra 😍 posts the most beautiful and rarest birds on the planet! Which is your favorite, from 1-10? 🌎
Follow @deepak_karra if you haven’t already

The featured birds are 
1. Pink Robin 
2. Rose Robin
3. Diamond Firetail
4. Spotted Pardalote
5. Rufous Fantail 
6. Superb Fairy-Wren 
7. Australian Ringneck 
8. Rainbow Lorikeet 
9. Scarlet Robin
10. Eastern Spinebill
